<h2>How to use the Open Journal Club?</h2>
<p>
Welcome to the Open Journal Club. This thread is meant for practice,
so that you can see how to leave comments and annotate pdf documents.
Feel free to leave irrelevant comments or discuss irrelevant topics
with participants, but stick to the elementary rules of mutual respect.
